      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "What about doing the whole `bandb.Write(ban map)` & `CNode::SetBannedSetDirty(false);` while holding `LOCK(cs_setBanned);`?\nOtherwise there will always be a possible race condition that someone is adding a ban after  `CNode::SetBannedSetDirty(false);` and before `bandb.Write(banmap)` or `CNode::GetBanned(banmap)`.\n",
      "commit_id" : "f4ac02ee7c6530c273503d8575a492e9b2ac1f13",
